      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さ～～ん！　お仕事\nお疲れ様でーす！　こころが癒やしてあげますよ～！",
      "startTime": 13.7939842796,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり今日も来たな、こころ。癒やすだなんて言って\nまた何か企んで……って、うおぉ、恐竜ぅ！？",
      "startTime": 22.0333334605,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_kaiju-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5099.9542158,
          "startTime": 23.4000000517
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "いけーい！　こころザウルス軍団とつげーーーーき！\n{user}さんをもぐもぐしちゃえ～！",
      "startTime": 30.7259189723,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "く、食われる……って、あれ、無事だ……\nあ、あの恐竜の群れは！？　どこへ消えた！？",
      "startTime": 38.9666667938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_kaiju-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 33.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふっ、映像に決まってるじゃないですか！\nララさんの発明品で作った立体映像ですよー！",
      "startTime": 46.9263041613,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "食べる一歩手前まで迫って驚かせる悪戯は\nモモちゃんのアイデアですけどね～！",
      "startTime": 54.492970828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったのか。本当に食われるかと思ったぞ\nまったく、こころとモモさんは相性抜群だな",
      "startTime": 61.5666667938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（俺にとっては災難でもあるな……）\n（二人が仲良くなってから悪戯三昧の毎日だ）",
      "startTime": 69.1333380382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（机の引き出しに大量の宇宙植物が入っていたり）\n（ララさんの発明品で俺の服を吸い取ろうとしたり）",
      "startTime": 76.4666713715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたんですか？　急に黙っちゃって\nあ！　もしかして本当は食べられたかったんですか？",
      "startTime": 82.6336112455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そんな訳ないだろう\nこんな悪戯、絶対俺以外にしちゃダメだからな",
      "startTime": 89.5666713715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "え～？　それってこころの悪戯を独り占めしたい\nってことですか？　もう、しょうがない人ですねぇ",
      "startTime": 98.3991216457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "安心して下さい。モモちゃんと考えた刺激の強い悪戯は\n{user}さんにしかしてませんから！",
      "startTime": 107.4657883123,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "それを聞いて少し安心したよ\nその調子で、俺にもしないでくれると助かるんだが……",
      "startTime": 113.4000047048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "ではでは、こころはこれから\nモモちゃんと悪戯会議があるので～！",
      "startTime": 119.391117171,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
